com.example.mac.bugfree

Class MoodEventList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.mac.bugfree.module.MoodEventList

  • public class MoodEventList
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by mac on 2017-02-25. An ArrayList Stores a series of moodEvents. A moodEvent can be add to, found from, delete from a MoodEventList(MEL) All moodEvents in current MEL can be sort by date using the sortByDate method.
